<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist nehst von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigisten
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        künig, ein brief <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daran uns sein küniglich
                        gnade <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie er
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den <expan>kurfürst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und verbottschaft hab, zu seinen
                                <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> gen Presslaw zu
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> xiiii tag vor
                                <expan>weyhenn<ex>achten</ex></expan> schierist und
                                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>erber</add>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> auch dahin <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also tun wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                        unser erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate dahin meynen zu
                                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir uns bey disem
                                <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> in guter
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, als vil ewch
                                <expan>füklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey, ob ewch von dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> künig,
                        auch also brief <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> sey und ob ir ewr
                            <add>erber</add>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch dahin meynet zu
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und auf welh zeit die auszreiten
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> wol getrawen. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Andree
                        <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
